quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  22,58,Wa Al-Ladhīna Hājarū Fī Sabīli Allāhi Thumma Qutilū 'Aw Mātū Layarzuqannahumu Allāhu Rizqāan Ĥasanāan Wa 'Inna Allāha Lahuwa Khayru Ar-Rāziqīna
  22,59,Layudkhilannahum Mudkhalāan Yarđawnahu Wa 'Inna Allāha La`alīmun Ĥalīmun
  22,60,Dhālika Wa Man `Āqaba Bimithli Mā `Ūqiba Bihi Thumma Bughiya `Alayhi Layanşurannahu Allāhu 'Inna Allāha La`afūwun Ghafūrun
  22,61,Dhālika Bi'anna Allāha Yūliju Al-Layla Fī An-Nahāri Wa Yūliju An-Nahāra Fī Al-Layli Wa 'Anna Allāha Samī`un Başīrun
  22,62,Dhālika Bi'anna Allāha Huwa Al-Ĥaqqu Wa 'Anna Mā Yad`ūna Min Dūnihi Huwa Al-Bāţilu Wa 'Anna Allāha Huwa Al-`Alīyu Al-Kabīru
  22,63,Alam Tará 'Anna Allāha 'Anzala Mina As-Samā'i Mā'an Fatuşbiĥu Al-'Arđu Mukhđarratan 'Inna Allāha Laţīfun Khabīrun
  22,64,Lahu Mā Fī As-Samāwāti Wa Mā Fī Al-'Arđi Wa 'Inna Allāha Lahuwa Al-Ghanīyu Al-Ĥamīdu